name: SendigOS
body:
## Welcome to SendigOS Operating System Source Code page! ##

You can find the code of the operating system using the Linux kernel coding here.

We work as a fully open source.
All of them share the code with you.
Our operating system is always up to date and stable work!
It does not include the error.

+ Open Source!
+ Free!
+ Decided!
+ Unique Design!
+ Current!
+ Fast!
+ Source No need!

We are carrying out this work with a team of 11 people unique. Did you know you can reach us every time? We are working with end users. We publish the new version in accordance with your request.

We're free!

### Team Members and Duties

+ Murat Kozan: Project Manager, Expert Python
+ Josh Rowe: Assistant Director, C ++ Developer, Design Specialist
+ Rylie Bourne: System Administrator
+ Hakan Taş: Software Developer
+ Gürcan Derici: Software Developer
+ Alyson Greene: Software Developer
+ Sabri Yılmaz : Software Developer
+ ADAM Searan: Translation Specialist
+ Marissa Bennet: Visual Programming Expert
+ Brandon Maddox: Resource Specialist
+ Holly Horn: Visual Design Expert
